  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5839011/" class="title-link">很好的基础书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5839011"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/echoecho8989/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2193973-6.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/echoecho8989/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">长着小雀斑的姑娘</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-04-09"
      class="main-meta">2013-04-09 16:58:46</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5839011_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这本书是必须要看的陶瓷类教课书，应该和冯先铭的《中国陶瓷》配套看。此本着重于陶瓷的发展历史。冯老的那本着重于鉴定，比较简略。建议先看完硅酸盐出的这本，再看冯老的那本。对于想了解陶瓷史发展的人来说是本不错的读物。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
